Yesterday Hannah, Adrienne, Katie, Tim, Joey,Courtney  and I went shopping at the Outlets. It was SOOOO much fun! 

I didn't get anything...

after we were done shopping, hannah, katie, and i rode this mini merry-go-round. It was so funny, too bad we didnt have a camera. After that Joey and I were sitting on the ground throwing rocks at each other. Some lady reported us to security and the security lady came while we were riding the merry-go-round thing. It was funny.     

then we all crammed into joey's car and were talking about how that if Katie fell out of the car it would be really funny


LOVE YOU KATIE

now i'm really bored.what are we DOING TODAY?

Graduation was most definately awesome.. except the actual graduation ceremony part

After the whole ceremony we had a limo. It was totally wicked hott. ((White Escalade)) We totally listened to the Spice Girls.

We went to Mellow and HHIC.

It was so much fun.

Saturday we were supposed to have a party at the PH pool but there were like 100 other people there.. so we had it at Hannah's house.
Courtney, Brianna, and I slept over at Hannah's house and had wicked fun. ((Joey and Tim hung around til like 11)) We stayed up until like 4:30. 

Then Hannah and I went to the mall. ((Tim and Joey showed up too)) I got this hott shirt thing, 2 CDs, and a lil gift for Katie. HAnnah got a HOTT shirt with blue and white stripes with a gold anchor on it. We are such hotties!

Its summer..
